---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="dao chau · uses"
  description="The apps, desk things and small configurations of Dao's ordinary day."
>
  <main class="shell" data-screen-label="uses">

    <!-- identity rail -->
    <aside class="rail">
      <svg class="mark" viewBox="0 0 132 64" role="img" aria-label="Goggle mark">
        <rect x="0" y="27" width="30" height="11" rx="3" fill="#f3c02c"/>
        <rect x="102" y="27" width="30" height="11" rx="3" fill="#f3c02c"/>
        <circle cx="66" cy="32" r="29" fill="#1d3450"/>
        <circle cx="66" cy="32" r="24" fill="#f7f8fa"/>
        <circle cx="66" cy="32" r="13" fill="#3a5a8c"/>
        <circle cx="66" cy="32" r="6" fill="#161616"/>
        <circle cx="62.5" cy="28.5" r="2.6" fill="#f7f8fa"/>
      </svg>

      <div class="id-block">
        <h1 class="id-name"><a href="/"><span class="w">dao</span><span class="w">chau</span></a></h1>
        <p class="id-role">uses · the dotfiles</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rail-divider"></div>

      <nav aria-label="Sections">
        <ul class="nav">
          <li><a href="/"><span class="n">cd</span><span class="t">~ home</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="#bin"><span class="n">01</span><span class="t">bin</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="#hardware"><span class="n">02</span><span class="t">hardware</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="#env"><span class="n">03</span><span class="t">env</span></a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <div class="rail-foot">
        <div class="rail-links">
          <a href="mailto:bichdao.chau@gmail.com">
            <span class="ic">@</span><span class="lbl">bichdao.chau@gmail.com</span>
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/daomapsieucap" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span class="ic">↗</span><span class="lbl">github</span>
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dao-chau" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span class="ic">↗</span><span class="lbl">linkedin</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="status">
          <span class="pulse"></span> based in saigon · idle, mostly · powered by cà phê sữa đá
        </p>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <!-- content column -->
    <div class="content">

      <p class="prompt"><b>dao@chau</b>:~$ <span class="cmd">dao --uses</span><span class="cur" aria-hidden="true"></span></p>

      <h2 class="hero">dotfiles, <em class="ln">the personal runtime.</em></h2>
      <p class="hero-sub">everything I actually reach for in a day, written down.</p>

      <!-- BIN -->
      <section id="bin" aria-labelledby="s-bin">
        <h3 class="sec" id="s-bin">
          <span class="dot"></span>
          <span class="lab"><span class="php">&lt;?</span>BIN</span>
          <span class="line"></span>
          <span class="num">01</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="sec-note">the current stack. pinned, not locked.</p>
        <dl class="kv">
          <dt>$ ide</dt>
          <dd>PhpStorm. <em>it has seen things inside functions.php.</em></dd>
          <dt>$ notes</dt>
          <dd>Obsidian. <em>I write things down so I can forget them safely.</em></dd>
          <dt>$ browser</dt>
          <dd>Brave. <em>switched once. no rollback.</em></dd>
        </dl>
      </section>

      <!-- HARDWARE -->
      <section id="hardware" aria-labelledby="s-hardware">
        <h3 class="sec" id="s-hardware">
          <span class="dot"></span>
          <span class="lab"><span class="php">&lt;?</span>HARDWARE</span>
          <span class="line"></span>
          <span class="num">02</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="sec-note">the hardware half. runs until it dies.</p>
        <dl class="kv">
          <dt>$ laptop</dt>
          <dd>Lenovo ThinkPad T14. <em>the company's, technically.</em></dd>
          <dt>$ pc</dt>
          <dd>Dell XPS 8700. <em>still running.</em></dd>
          <dt>$ display</dt>
          <dd>Dell U2417H.</dd>
          <dt>$ keyboard</dt>
          <dd>Logitech K120. <em>simple, but it works.</em></dd>
          <dt>$ mouse</dt>
          <dd>Logitech MX Anywhere 3, with a Hyperwork Silentium S01 on quiet duty.</dd>
          <dt>$ phone</dt>
          <dd>Samsung S24.</dd>
          <dt>$ tablet</dt>
          <dd>Samsung Tab A9. <em>runs Netflix. tests breakpoints.</em></dd>
          <dt>$ ereader</dt>
          <dd>Kindle Paperwhite 4. <em>where the reading actually happens.</em></dd>
          <dt>$ headphone</dt>
          <dd>Sony WH-1000XM4. <em>noise cancelling on, world off.</em></dd>
          <dt>$ earphone</dt>
          <dd>Samsung Galaxy Buds 3 FE.</dd>
        </dl>
      </section>

      <!-- ENV -->
      <section id="env" aria-labelledby="s-env">
        <h3 class="sec" id="s-env">
          <span class="dot"></span>
          <span class="lab"><span class="php">&lt;?</span>ENV</span>
          <span class="line"></span>
          <span class="num">03</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="sec-note">day-to-day runtime config.</p>
        <dl class="kv">
          <dt>$ music</dt>
          <dd>Spotify. <em>quiet enough to read over.</em></dd>
          <dt>$ downtime</dt>
          <dd>Netflix. <em>research, obviously.</em></dd>
          <dt>$ fuel</dt>
          <dd>cà phê sữa đá. <em>a constant, not a variable.</em></dd>
          <dt>$ noise_level</dt>
          <dd>low. <em>a book nearby, nobody else in the room.</em></dd>
        </dl>
      </section>

      <p class="colophon"><span class="c">#</span>nothing here is impressive; all of it is mine.</p>
      <p class="exit"><b>dao@chau</b>:~$ <span class="cmd"><a href="/">cd ~</a></span><span class="cur" aria-hidden="true"></span></p>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
